homework 1.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.onfleet.demo.homework
Contains RouteCalculator and associated objects, for a demo take-home interview problem assigned to Sam Gammon by OnFleet.
com.onfleet.demo.homework.collection
Holds collection-style objects related to the RouteCalculator homework problem.
com.onfleet.demo.homework.struct
Holds structures that are used as data by the RouteCalculator for the OnFleet homework problem.
com.onfleet.demo.homework.util
Supplies utilities involved with testing and/or executing the demo RouteCalculator homework problem for OnFleet.
